            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;You inspired me to create an enhanced version that allows bracket notation &amp;amp; property names with spaces as well as validating the inputs: &lt;a href=&quot;https://it.knightnet.org.uk/kb/node-js/get-properties/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;it.knightnet.org.uk/kb/node-js/get-properties&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

