            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I love this solution. However I&apos;m trying to modify the values in the original object, it seems your function returns a sub copy of the object. Is it possible to change it so that modifying the returned object modifies the original ?&lt;/span&gt;

