            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;There are many situations, such as deep nested object lookups, where this is the only option.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1636704/jonathan-kempf&quot; title=&quot;699 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Jonathan Kempf&lt;/a&gt;
