                        &lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@Luke He&apos;s now the only want to bring Lodash &lt;code&gt;_.get&lt;/code&gt; to the table. I think this answer deserves now upvotes instead of downvotes. It may be overkill, but it&apos;s good to know it exists.&lt;/span&gt;

